list.abstract: each（英 [iːtʃ]，美 [iːtʃ]），英语单词，作限定词为每；各；各自。作副词为对各个；对每个。例句：Students should be able to extend the logic of each to their particular circumstance.（学生应该能够将每个人的逻辑延伸到他们的特定环境。） each的近义词有respective，several，apiece。
《Each》是张亦赤演唱的一首歌曲，由张亦赤、RJ作词、作曲，收录于张亦赤2018年8月8日发行的专辑《Each》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Each airport's control tower guides each plane to take off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个机场的控制塔能指导每架飞机起飞。

yingyinNormal.en: Each loss is unbearable, but when it's someone you know...
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个生命都弥足珍贵，尤其是你熟悉的生命。

yingyinNormal.en: But I look forward to getting to know each and every one of you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很希望认识你们每个人。

yingyinNormal.en: Each puzzle will lead you to the location of the next.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个谜题将会指引诸位去下一个地点。

yingyinNormal.en: Each person's landing pod had enough life support for two years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个人的着陆舱里携带着两年的补给。

yingyinNormal.en: Each of us has a code for our optimal physical condition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们每个人都有自己身体最佳状况的遗传密码。

yingyinNormal.en: We've become alienated from each other. Each one an island onto himself, concerned only with ourselves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们都互相疏远了，每个人都活在自己的世界里，只关心自己的问题。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: I say this I shall stand for him as he has for each of you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我说我会支持他，一如他支持你们每个人一样。

yingyinNormal.en: First thing I'm going to do is hear motions from each of the defendants' lawyers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先我要听取每个辨方律师的诉讼请求。

yingyinNormal.en: When I blow my whistle, I want each of you to kick off from the ground, hard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一吹哨子，你们每个人都用力蹬地，腾空。

yingyinNormal.en: And each one needs fuel so it can supply power 365 days a year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个电站都要消耗能量，所以才能1年365天不间断供电。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I'm glad to have shared in you perils, Thorin, each and every one of them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很高兴能和你患难与共，索林，和你们每个人。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: State funeral. Must-attend event for western leaders. Each one a target.
yingyinNormal.zh: 国葬仪式，西方领导人必定出席的事件，每个人都是目标。

yingyinNormal.en: At the end of each stage of training, the lowestranking initiates will be leaving us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 训练的每个阶段，排名倒数的新生们将会离开无畏派。

yingyinNormal.en: Each of these spinning points of light represents the readings from thousands of sensors.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其中每个旋转的光点都是成千上万的传感器发出的。

yingyinNormal.en: When mankind discovers who we are, what we can do, each of us will face a choice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等人类发现我们，我们的能力，我们每个人就会面临选择。

yingyinNormal.en: So, I am grateful to each and every one of you for coming out and showing your support today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我很感激你们每个人今天前来表示对我的支持。

yingyinNormal.en: If I could, I would run each and every one of you viewers up a flagpole and salute you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果可以，你们每个人都是我升上去后愿意敬礼的旗帜。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, so each welcome bag gets a schedule of events, a map, and chocolate from me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个迎宾礼袋中含有一张婚礼时间表，一份地图和我送的巧克力。

yingyinNormal.en: And each core memory powers a different aspect of Riley's personality. Like. Hockey Island.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每个核心记忆都会强化莱莉个性的某个方面，比如，冰球岛。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: every one of two or more individuals considered separately

examination_example.sentence: "<highlight>Each</highlight> book opens up new avenues of knowledge to explore", Gates says.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 盖茨说:“每本书都开辟了新的知识探索途径。”

examination_example.sentence: Then increase it at a higher rate <highlight>each</highlight> year and essentially try to generate additional revenue.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然后每年以更高的速度增加，并基本上试图创造额外的收入。

examination_example.sentence: As such, it needed to appreciate the economic realities, the social contexts and power relations in which <highlight>each</highlight> epoch stood.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，它需要理解每个时代所处的经济现实、社会背景和权力关系。

examination_example.sentence: We neither understand nor respect <highlight>each</highlight> other, and we have no basis for compromise or cooperation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们既不理解也不尊重对方，我们没有妥协或合作的基础。

examination_example.sentence: Now we can understand <highlight>each</highlight> other's positions and recognize our shared values, since we both care about needy workers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在我们可以理解彼此的立场，并认识到我们共同的价值观，因为我们都关心贫困的工人。

examination_example.sentence: Ideally, different kinds of reading inform <highlight>each</highlight> other, and act as useful reference points for and counterbalances to one another.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 理想情况下，不同类型的阅读相互影响，并作为有用的参考点，相互平衡。

word_usage.usage: each作代词，用作主语时，如果强调“个别”，其谓语动词通常用单数形式，如：Each of the answers is worth 20 points.；如果each强调的是“集体”，或先行词的主语是复数时，其谓语动词则用复数形式，如：We each have our own car.

direction_info.description:

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: every one of two or more individuals considered separately

examination_example.sentence: If your model of reality is wildly different from the actual world, then you struggle to take effective actions <highlight>each</highlight> day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你的现实模式与现实世界大不相同，那么你每天都很难采取有效的行动。

examination_example.sentence: Then they could compare outcomes for <highlight>each</highlight> group.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然后他们可以比较每组的结果。

examination_example.sentence: The authors combined data from 558 prior surveys that <highlight>each</highlight> measured one or more of Hofstede's cultural dimensions.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作者综合了558项先前调查的数据，每项调查都测量了Hofstede的一个或多个文化维度。

examination_example.sentence: However, conflict between characters is often depicted with characters being unkind to <highlight>each</highlight> other.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，角色之间的冲突经常被描绘成角色之间互相不友好。

examination_example.sentence: There are two main groups of bats, which are believed to have evolved independently of <highlight>each</highlight> other, but both from a common ancestor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 蝙蝠有两大类，据信它们是独立进化的，但都来自同一个祖先。

examination_example.sentence: "Americans don't talk to <highlight>each</highlight> other, we entertain <highlight>each</highlight> other," Postman wrote.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “美国人不互相交谈，我们互相娱乐，”波兹曼写道。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: every one of two or more individuals considered separately

examination_example.sentence: According to one study, <highlight>each</highlight> high school graduate contributes at least 500,000 dollars to the local economy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据一项研究，每个高中毕业生为当地经济贡献了至少50万美元。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Each</highlight> artist has their own individual style but all artists share a common aim: to draw attention to the pollution in our cities.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每位艺术家都有自己的风格，但所有艺术家都有一个共同的目标：引起人们对城市污染的关注。

examination_example.sentence: Watch television no more than 3 hours <highlight>each</highlight> day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每天看电视不超过3小时。

examination_example.sentence: But we believed in <highlight>each</highlight> other and our faith made us strong.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但我们彼此信任，我们的信仰使我们变得强大。

examination_example.sentence: They are also spending more time working with <highlight>each</highlight> other rather than reporting upwards.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们也花更多的时间相互合作，而不是向上汇报。

examination_example.sentence: This would be an environment in which teachers and students actually knew <highlight>each</highlight> other.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这将是一个老师和学生真正了解彼此的环境。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Even soccer fans tend to have a seat <highlight>each</highlight>; gone are the days of thousands standing to watch the match.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 即使是足球迷也倾向于每人有一个座位；成千上万人站着看比赛的日子已经一去不复返了。

examination_example.sentence: For postcrossing to work worldwide, a common communication language is needed so that everyone can understand <highlight>each</highlight> other.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了让明信片交流在全球范围内发挥作用，需要一种通用的交流语言，以便每个人都能相互理解。

examination_example.sentence: Astronauts spend hours cleaning them up <highlight>each</highlight> week.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 宇航员每周都要花几个小时来清理它们。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: To make friends with <highlight>each</highlight> other.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 彼此交朋友。

examination_example.sentence: As they thought about this possibility, they all began to treat <highlight>each</highlight> other with strong respect (尊重).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当他们想到这种可能性时，他们都开始以强烈的尊重对待彼此。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Each</highlight> group had a task to raise money for the disabled.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每个小组都有一项为残疾人筹集资金的任务。

word_usage.usage:
each单独用作主语或修饰主语时，谓语动词要用第三人称单数形式。
如：Two boys entered. Each was carrying a suitcase.
两个男孩进来，每人提着一个手提箱。
There are 250 blocks of stone, and each one weighs a ton.
有250块石头，每块重一吨。（朗文考试）

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: each侧重个别的情况，each可以作形容词和代词，each可以用于两者或两者以上的人或物。
every侧重全体，有“所有的”之意，every只能作形容词，every则用于三者或三者以上的人或物。
